{"tid":1649074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［舊職業］裝飾師","createTime":"2019-10-12T13:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T14:28:34.000Z","uid":282293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6ad2049bfe060668ecca0b315fdae4c6cc6315","tid":1649074,"uid":282293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"講咗咁耐話要裝飾，咁耐以嚟見過嘅次數都唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明件事好簡單，都係無乜人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為咗令實現全民裝飾同埋令受眾更廣，以下有兩個建議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全民裝飾</span><br />\n身為一個裝飾師，其實只要有文宣喺身就夠。想成為高級裝飾師嘅話，就要買埋噴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經過要裝修或者裝飾嘅舖頭，裝飾師鍾意擺啲文宣喺舖頭前面地下又得，痴喺舖頭又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之每個人帶定啲文宣就實冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重現長輩圖</span><br />\n早幾個月大家明明知道長輩圖嘅威力有幾勁，點解最近又唔見哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多時候得深黃知道裝修嘅原因，有啲冇連登冇TG嘅老一輩係唔知點解㗎，加上長輩圖獨一無二嘅吸引力，一定可以更入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望有人會整吓呢類嘅長輩圖啦，同埋裝修嘅外語文宣都要多啲<br />\n<br />\n記住連登只係其中一個媒介，唔係個個都知我地做緊咩。見到裝修嘅時候，就攞起你嘅文宣走過去放低或者黐住啦。有記者嘅時候，就更加要攞多啲文宣過去。下次我唔要淨係聽到「開遮、開遮」，重要聽到「要文宣、要文宣」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時化革命</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次開po，有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKtGDKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKtGDKS.jpg&h=4ea7d6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzJ7zid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzJ7zid.jpg&h=e8b2866b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKuVJbz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKuVJbz.jpg&h=6fa76a31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pKq5pV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pKq5pV.jpg&h=2f33297b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUK27Dg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUK27Dg.jpg&h=b241dd2e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Fyvw4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Fyvw4X.jpg&h=553d3135&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJpbgwE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJpbgwE.jpg&h=fd000958&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b578dd3c0a82369acced879935db5f20ad7e34e","tid":1649074,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6f28809094bc5ae6a0aedc60a1252f52a586e0f","tid":1649074,"uid":282293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n打錯，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa6d0f482a7cd46a358143ae185a318079307af","tid":1649074,"uid":282293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89157bc22e03cb0cc4f878aa4122c572ffa8315","tid":1649074,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"長輩圖好殺食，起碼引到d阿叔阿嬋望下"},{"pid":"538292124046119a8541dfc3d4611a1bc733b771","tid":